      "writtenOn": "2020-03-04T14:34:58Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "We use the bit depth of the destination.\n\nDithering at the very end, after blending with the destination value, probably leads to higher quality dithering but is would be prohibitively expensive/not feasible on the GPU unfortunately (it would basically be as if every blend were an advanced blend that needed to have access to the dst color in the shader).",
