      "writtenOn": "2020-03-04T14:40:12Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I\u0027m thinking, if we do want to change anything like this, let\u0027s only do it by deleting features?  As long as the user can produce these effects using a compound shader, there\u0027s no need for us to legislate where the colorization or alpha fold (or perhaps dither) happen statically in the pipeline.",
      "parentUuid": "0949fc27_32a0735e",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 44,
        "startChar": 41,
        "endLine": 44,
        "endChar": 54
      },
